Production:
1. go to project directory with parameters:
2. building:
mvn install -DserverContext=/server -DserverPort=8085
3. run application

Development (default start app):
0. build & install node,npm by mvn, go to project directory:
mvn install -DserverContext=/server -DserverPort=8085
1. go to src\main\resources\static
2. build dev:
.\node\npm run dev
3. run dev hot reloading server:
.\node\npm run start

PS: You can define own scripts with another parameters in package.json file
